<head>
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Reenie+Beanie' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Mamajamas</title>
<meta name="description" content="">
<%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", :media => "all" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
<%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body>
<!-- header area ***** -->
<div id="hed-wrap">
  <div class="gridContainer clearfix">
    <div id="header">
      <div id="branding">
        <h1>Mamajamas</h1>
      </div>
      <div id="search">
      	<input type="text" placeholder="Search">
      </div>
      <div id="login">
        <ul>
        <% if user_signed_in? -%>
          <li>
            Hello, <strong><%= link_to current_user.username, edit_user_registration_path %></strong>
          </li>
          <li>
            <%= link_to "Logout", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %>
          </li>
        <% else -%>
          <li>
          <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, :id => "signup" %>
          </li>
          <li>
            <%= link_to "Login", new_user_session_path %>
          </li>
        <% end -%>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="progress">
      	<ol>
        	<li><strong>1</strong> Take the quiz.</li>
            <li><strong>2</strong> Make your list and get advice.</li> 
            <li><strong>3</strong> Share your list.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- end header area --> 
<!-- body area ***** -->
<div class="gridContainer clearfix">
  <div id="title">
    <div id="subhed">
      <h2>Your baby gear list</h2>
    </div>
    <div id="title-links">[buttons]</div>
  </div>
  <div id="primary">
    <div class="content">[nav]</div>
  </div>
  <div id="secondary">
    <div class="content">[main content]
      <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
      <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
      <%= yield %>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc nibh libero, fermentum eget luctus consequat, mollis in libero. Donec tincidunt posuere sem. Etiam aliquam est sed mi accumsan porttitor. Pellentesque ac mattis tellus. Vivamus libero enim, sollicitudin vitae aliquam a, tempus eu arcu. Phasellus ante justo, bibendum sed vehicula a, aliquet at tortor. Nullam lacinia, ligula quis suscipit pharetra, risus mauris tincidunt lectus, quis congue diam sem eget arcu. Morbi nec tellus sodales purus pharetra iaculis. Proin convallis, odio nec auctor tristique, mauris odio tristique magna, tincidunt fermentum dui dolor ac nunc. Nulla tincidunt dapibus lorem hendrerit viverra. Cras porttitor nunc in mi ultricies viverra sagittis nunc pharetra. Duis lorem est, sollicitudin quis eleifend in, pharetra ut elit. Fusce vestibulum, mi ut blandit commodo, augue lorem ullamcorper risus, accumsan facilisis diam nulla sit amet dui. </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="tertiary">[tertiary]
    <div id="module-name">
      <div class="content">module content</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="footer">
    <div class="content">[footer]</div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- end body area --> 
<!-- modal window ************ -->
<% unless user_signed_in? -%>
  <div class="modal-wrap" style="display:none;" id="signup-modal">
    <div class="modal-overlay"> &nbsp; </div>
    <div class="vertical-offset"></div>
    <!-- modal window box -->
    <div class="modal-box" id="create-account">
      <%= render :partial => "devise/registrations/signup" %>
    </div>
    <!-- end modal window box --> 
  </div>
  <div class="modal-wrap" style="display:none;" id="email-signup-modal">
    <div class="modal-overlay"> &nbsp; </div>
    <div class="vertical-offset"></div>
    <!-- modal window box -->
    <div class="modal-box" id="create-account-email">
      <%= render :partial => "devise/registrations/email_signup_form" %>
    </div>
    <!-- end modal window box --> 
  </div>
<% end -%>
<!-- /end modal window ************ --> 

<!-- Google Analytics -->
</body>
</html>
